          li Theme Fonts: There are two theme fonts available at the top of the Font menu under Theme Fonts.
          img(src="images/applytheme/theme_understand_font.png")
      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
          li Theme Effects: These affect the preset shape styles. You can find shape styles on the Format tab whenever you select a shape or SmartArt graphic.
          img(src="images/applytheme/theme_element_effect.png")

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
