      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        h2 Modifying a shape or text box
        li When you click on a shape or text box, handles will appear that let you manipulate the shape. There are several types of handles:

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        li Sizing handles: Click, hold, and drag the sizing handles until the shape or text box is the desired size. You can use the corner sizing handles to change the height and width at the same time.
        img(src="images/shape/sw10.jpg")

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
