        img(src="images/shape/sw14.jpg")

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        h3 To change the shape style:
        li Choosing a Shape Style allows you to apply preset colors and effects to quickly change the appearance of your shape or text box.
        li Select the shape or text box you want to change.

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        li On the Format tab, click the More drop-down arrow in the Shape Styles group.
        img(src="images/shape/sw15.jpg")

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        li A drop-down menu of styles will appear. Select the style you want to use.
        img(src="images/shape/sw16.jpg")
        li The shape or text box will appear in the selected style.

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        h3 To change the shape fill color:
        li Select the shape or text box you want to change.
        li On the Format tab, click the Shape Fill drop-down arrow. The Shape Fill menu appears.

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        li Move the mouse over the various colors. Select the color you want to use. To view more color options, select More Fill Colors.
        img(src="images/shape/sw17.jpg")
        li The shape or text box will appear in the selected color.

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        h3 To change the shape outline:
        li Select the shape or text box you want to change.
        li On the Format tab, click the Shape Outline drop-down arrow. The Shape Outline menu will appear.

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
