        section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
           h2 Modifying charts with chart tools
           p There are many other ways to customize and organize your charts. For example, PowerPoint allows you to change the chart type, rearrange a chart's data, and even change the layout and style of a chart.

        section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
           h3 To change the chart type:
           p If you find that your data isn't well-suited to a certain chart, it's easy to switch to a new chart type. In our example, we'll change our chart from a line chart to a column chart.
           
        section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
