       section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
         img(src="images/slidemaster/master_text_compare.png")

       section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
         h2Creating new slide layouts
         p One of the most powerful features of Slide Master view is the option to create new slide layouts. This is an easy way to add interesting and unique slide layouts to an existing theme. You could even use this feature to design an entirely new theme, as in the example below.

       section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
