       section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
          h2 About hyperlinks
          p Hyperlinks have two basic parts: the address of the webpage, email address, or other location they are linking to, and the display text (which can also be a picture or shape). For example, the address could be http://www.youtube.com, and "YouTube" could be the display text. In some cases, the display text might be the same as the address. When you're creating a hyperlink in PowerPoint, you'll be able to choose both the address and the display text or image.

        section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
