         section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
            h3 Using shapes and pictures as hyperlinks
            p Sometimes you might want to to format objects—including shapes, text boxes, and pictures—as hyperlinks. This is especially helpful if you want the object to act like a button. To do this, simply right-click the desired object and select Hyperlink from the menu that appears. Click the object during the presentation to open the hyperlink.
